						<div class="postbody">I'm not very familiar with how plasmas work. But plasmas upscale to 480p or 720p or 1080p, so even if they did scan the picture sequentially like a CRT, I don't think the screen would activate the 15.7 kHz resonator for the same reason that a VGA monitor doesn't.</div>

