				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Do note that while checking for a hit horizontally requires you to brighten a specific area and darken the rest, obtaining the vertical position is much simpler as long as you're pointing at a non-black area. You can take advantage of this, by for example letting the volume be continuously controlled by the height of the zapper while the notes would be played by shooting at targets at discrete horizontal points.</div>

